{"tid":1035039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【六四30年】紀念碑美國LA建成 創作者望世人不要遺忘","createTime":"2019-02-24T11:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T09:14:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec80a900f66d110411a092f22786f3b6876a6d5","tid":1035039,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"全球最大的六四紀念碑在美國洛杉磯落成，近200名各界人士到場參與落成儀式。紀念碑的創作者、雕塑家陳維明稱，「我們不想遺忘30年前發生在六四的慘案，那是中國人心中的傷痛」。<br />\n六四紀念碑座落在連接洛杉磯與拉斯維加斯的15號州際公路，由「6」「4」兩個巨型數字組成，基座背面則刻有由天安門母親丁子霖收集的200多名六四死難者名字。陳維明表示，「這個雕塑本身高6.4米，加上2.5米的基座，剛好是8.9米，含義就是紀念89六四。這個公園離中國北京剛好是6,400英里，方位傾角是64度。」<br />\n對於樹立雕塑的目的，陳維明稱他們想以雕塑方式，保持人們對六四事件的記憶，並提醒世人永遠不要忘記中共獨裁政權的威脅。<br />\ntwitter/美國之音<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1550995847_0b2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1550995847_0b2f.jpg&h=f757944b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c29e83daef902f282a1627e0c98c88e99b4ad692","tid":1035039,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:53:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cd299e181be6eec0b3ce03df33ace2ae575bb28","tid":1035039,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:58:29.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"1a9866fb13d5c2134ea1b8004a92c86438bba0e8","tid":1035039,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T21:03:42.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"ed7d6469a072a52aad88842ee22034f00054f207","tid":1035039,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a9866fb13d5c2134ea1b8004a92c86438bba0e8","tid":1035039,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T21:03:42.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T21:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反咩 美國人反嘜"},{"pid":"c47a3f321416a97363983ea9c73f1ec82c0f9bce","tid":1035039,"uid":51411,"like":